      <title>最高法院在新任期内热衷于遏制美国机构权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/supreme-court-asked-to-curb-regulations-more-after-ending-chevron-deference</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国最高法院作出重磅裁决，削弱联邦机构监管企业的权力后，大政府的反对者们正在推行更加大胆的议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/supreme-court-asked-to-curb-regulations-more-after-ending-chevron-deference</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
